Class FloodFill

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Filters.FloodFill
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseInPlace

    public class FloodFill
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseInPlace
    Flood Fill filter. The purpose of Flood Fill is to color an entire area of connected pixels with the same color.
